# Frontend

## App Router

- `src/app/(auth)/` — login, signup, callback
- `src/app/(dashboard)/` — org-scoped app shell
- Route groups for layout sharing; dynamic `[orgSlug]`, `[projectId]`, `[deckId]`
- `loading.tsx` and `error.tsx` per major route segment

## Components

- **Server Components** for data fetching and static layout
- **Client Components** (`'use client'`) for interactivity: DnD, forms, editor, modals
- UI primitives in `components/ui/` (shadcn); feature components in `components/slides/`, `components/decks/`
- Use `cn()` from `lib/utils` for class merging

## Forms

- react-hook-form + Zod resolver
- Optimistic UI only where rollback is safe
- Toast feedback via `sonner`

## Slide editor

- Drag-and-drop reorder via `@dnd-kit`
- Layout picker maps to `SLIDE_LAYOUTS` from `src/types/slide.ts`
- Preview must match export layout semantics

## Do not

- Fetch secrets or service-role data in client components
- Use `useEffect` for data that belongs in Server Components
- Inline styles; use Tailwind + design tokens from DESIGN.md
